.TH NOMNOMUS 1 "June 2026" "nomnomus 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
nomnomus \- track daily calories and macronutrients
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nomnomus
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B nomnomus
opens a GTK 4 and Libadwaita nutrient tracker designed for narrow Linux
phone screens.
.PP
The application stores its local SQLite data under
.IR $XDG_DATA_HOME/nomnomus/data.sqlite3 .
.SH FEATURES
The application supports editable daily goals, monthly summaries, Open Food
Facts searches, and optional camera-based barcode scanning.
